propertyName: Dollar General Portfolio- Fisher and Fosston

rptwservicerwatchlistirp.commentActionToBeTaken: The loan is secured by a 42,808 sf office property located in Houston, TX. The property was built in 1982 and renovated in 2008. At UW, DSCR was 1.63x at 86.9% occupancy. 10/30/17: Q3 2016 DSCR was -0.05x at 61.34% occupancy, compared to 1.29x at 82.59% occupancy for YE 2016. Performance at this property has seen a decline after losing several tenants at the beginning of 2017. In order to improve occupancy at the property, the borrower is having their leasing team work with third-party brokers. They are, however, having difficulties finding new tenants for the vacancies.

propertyName: Dollar General Portfolio- Osakis and Adrian

rptwservicerwatchlistirp.commentActionToBeTaken: The loan is secured by a 128 unit lodging property that is located in Bothell, WA and was built in 2010. At UW, DSCR was 1.79x with 77.2% occupancy. 8/29/2017: Q2 2017 YTD DSCR was 1.14x with 74.05% occupancy, compared to 1.44x at YE 2016 with 76.97% occupancy. The low YTD DSCR is attributable to seasonality at the property. Q1 and Q4 are historically the poorest performing quarters, whereas Q2 sees better business and Q3 is the peak time of the year. Due to this, the YTD DSCR begins quite low and improves as the year progresses.

The loan is secured by a 101 unit lodging property located in Austin, TX. It was built in 1997 and renovated in 2016. At UW, DSCR was 1.81x at 71.3% occupancy. 10/2/17: Q2 2017 YTD DSCR was 1.21x at 57.06% occupancy, compared to the YE 2016 DSCR of 1.55x at 68.5% occupancy. While the ADR has remained in-line with previous periods, lower occupancy this year has hurt performance at the property. The cause of the occupancy issue has been ongoing PIP at the property, which resulted in 30% rooms being under renovation and unavailable to rent. This, coupled with what the borrower stated as a slow January in Austin, has led to the revenue decrease seen this year. Per the borrower, performance should pick up the rest of the year, when the renovations are complete.
